dct_title_s: Donald W. Hamer Center for Maps and Geospatial Information Digital Map Drawer of Penn State Rare Maps
dct_description_sm: The Donald W. Hamer Center for Maps and Geospatial Information digital map drawer contains the subset of our physical map collection that has been digitized and is not protected by licensing or copyright. It includes historical maps from around the world and an assortment of other historical Pennsylvania maps.
